title: [Nanetta's Cafe, Dining Room]
description: The sound of crickets and late night revelers drift occasionally through an open window.  Yellow checked curtains rustle lightly with each passing of the cool evening breeze.  Cozy scrollworked iron tables are tucked against the walls, leaving a clear pathway to the cashier's counter.  A menu board, handwritten in delicate script, presents the daily specials.  The sweet aroma of freshly baked pies drifts through an open doorway near the back.
